==Notable accidents and incidents==
* On December 9, 1999, a CH-46D Sea Knight, Naval Bureau Number 154790 assigned to Marine Medium Helicopter Squadron 166 (HMM-166) crashed during a boarding exercise off the coast of San Diego, California, killing 7 US marines.&lt;ref&gt;http://www.check-six.com/Crash_Sites/SeaKnight-USMC-1999.htm&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EoHd5LePyVc&lt;/ref&gt;

